== Description == * This is not a role handed out as a card, but rather the first [[Werewolf]] to die becomes a [[Ghost]] or [[Fading Ghost]], but they are restricted to speaking for only 30 seconds after every defense and are the last to be heard before the vote. Wakes up with wolves at night, but their choice is ignored by moderator.
