{| class="wikitable" |- | '''Role''' || Mystery Lycan |- | '''Expansion''' || N/A |- | '''Designer''' || [[User:Aaron94132|Aaron Newman]], Jess McCartney |- | '''Value''' || +8 |- | '''Team''' || Villager |- | '''Appears to Seer as''' || Villager |- | '''Night Active''' || Yes |}
== Description == * Every night the moderator will wake the whore and ask all other players to raise their hand if they want to sleep with the whore. The whore must pick one player who has their hand raised and who they have not yet slept with, otherwise the whore sleeps alone. Whoever the whore chooses can not be killed that night. If the whore chooses a werewolf the whore will die, in addition to whoever the werewolves choose as their victim. Everyone who raised their hand will not vote the next day (take off shoe or put a stone on their card). The whore may once choose herself and give up the right to vote to appear as a patron.
