== Description == * Every night targets a player for black magic attack. ** If target is a special role, villager or werewolf, that role loses their ability and is informed when they try to use it. ** If target is a werewolf, the werewolf becomes a [[Minion]] * Wins when there are no werewolves that can kill at night or roles with special abilities.
